7 An Act relating to alien ownership of land; amending
60 O.S. 2021, Section 122, which relates to
8 exceptions; defining terms; modifying exception;
updating statutory language; making language gender
9 neutral; and declaring an emergency.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 60 O.S. 2021, Section 122, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 122. A. For purposes of this section:
16 1. “Bona fide resident” shall mean a lawful permanent resident
17 of the United States; and
18 2. “Lawful permanent resident” shall mean a foreign national
19 who has been granted the right to reside permanently in the United
20 States.
21 B. This article shall not apply to lands now owned in this
22 state by aliens so long as they are held by the present owners, nor
23 to any alien who is or shall take up become, within one (1) year, a
24 bona fide residence in resident of this state:; and any alien who is
