1 or s hall become, within one (1) year, a bona fide resident of the
2 State of Oklahoma this state shall have the right to acquire and
3 hold lands in this state upon the same terms as citizens United
4 States citizen residents of the State of Oklahoma this state during
5 the continuance of such bona fide residence of such alien in this
6 state:. Provided, that if any such resident alien shall cease to be
7 a bona fide inhabitant resident of this state, such alien shall have
8 five (5) years one (1) year from the time he or she ceased to be
9 such bona fide resident in which to alienate such lands.
10 SECTION 2. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
11 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
12 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
13 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
